706763f-c.title: Brooklyn: Shore Parkway - Plumb 1st Street
706763f-c.text:
Shore Parkway, east from about Pluhb 1st Street,
showing this Brooklyn section of the Belt Parkway, former-
1y known as the Circumferential Parkway, under constructinn.
Much of this parkway was built on hydraulic fill taken from
Sheepshead Bay.
View 1: July 9, 1936
Views 2,3: June 13, 1940
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTION1
